David Guetta - Listen (Album)(2014) 

                  EDM, Electro House, Electropop | Parlophone UK

                256 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 00:47:11 | 92 Mb



The year 2014 again under the sign Guetta! Always on top, the boss of electro / dance in the world is there with his new album! More personal, pop, hard fact of tubes as only he knows how to make. Includes singles Lovers On The Sun and Dangerous! Bebe Rexha, South African male choral group Ladysmith Black Mambazo, Ms. Dynamite, Elliphant, Birdy, Jaymes Young, Sonny Wilson, Vassy, and Skylar Grey. It also features additional production from his frequent collaborator Giorgio Tuinfort, Avicii, Afrojack, Nicky Romero, Showtek and Stadiumx among others, with additional writing credits from Jason Evigan, Alicia Keys and The-Dream among others.
